<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002599>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Delopleurus spp. (A) D. fossatus sp. nov., lateral view of body (sinuate epipleuron is arrowed); (B–D) anterior tibiae: (B) D. pullus, male; (C) D. pullus, female; (D) D.naviauxi, female, holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002599/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002611>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Delopleurus fossatus sp. nov. (A, D) habitus (A, male, D, female); (B, E) pygidium (B, male, E, female); (C) aedeagus in lateral view and internal sac; (F) locality map." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002611/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002615>
    dc:description "Figure 9. Delopleurus spp. and Metacatharsius janssensi. (A, E) habitus (A, D. striatus, E, M. janssensi); (B) D. striatus, head and pronotum in dorsal view; (C) D. striatus, pygidium; (D) D. striatus, locality map; (F) D. fossatus sp. nov., ventral view of head showing gula with distinct longitudinal groove." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002615/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002601>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Delopleurus spp. (A, D) habitus; (B, E) pygidium; (F) aedeagus in lateral view and internal sac; (C, G) locality maps. (A–C) D. naviauxi sp. nov.; (D–G) D. pubescens sp. nov." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002601/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002603>
    dc:description "Figure 3. Delopleurus pullus. (A, D) habitus (A, male, D, female); (B, E) pygidium (B, male, E, female); (C) aedeagus in lateral view and internal sac; (F) locality map." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002603/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002605>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Delopleurus darrenmanni sp. nov. (A, D) habitus (A, male, D, female); (B, E) pygidium (B, male, E, female); (C) aedeagus in lateral view and internal sac; (F) locality map." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002605/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002607>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Delopleurus gilleti. (A, D) habitus (A, male, D, female); (B, E) pygidium (B, male, E, female); (C) aedeagus in lateral view and internal sac; (F) locality map." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002607/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002609>
    dc:description "Figure 6. Delopleurus krikkeni sp. nov., holotype. (A) habitus; (B) pygidium; (C) aedeagus in lateral view and internal sac; (D) locality map." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4002609/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4002613>
    dc:description "Figure 8. Delopleurus parvus. (A, D) habitus (A, male, D, female); (B, E) pygidium (B, male, E, female); (C) aedeagus in lateral view and internal sac; (F) locality map." ;
